document.full_text: oil prices dipped slightly in choppy, thin trade on friday as traders weighed concerns about middle east unrest and libya's conflict as well as demand for oil in quake-hit japan and debt-laden europe.
document.title: oil slips, but choppy eyeing demand, supply threats
